behind all the recent shootings.

184
00:16:34,868 --> 00:16:39,164
As you can see,
South Korea is no longer safe from guns.

185
00:16:39,248 --> 00:16:40,332
So I have…

186
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:41,834
