241
00:20:47,371 --> 00:20:49,081
-Give me one first.
-I'll buy one too.

242
00:20:52,167 --> 00:20:53,710
Give me a sec, all right?

243
00:20:53,794 --> 00:20:56,922
Long-suppressed sociopathic tendencies

244
00:20:57,756 --> 00:21:01,134
